    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, increase the heat to high and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, reduce the heat to medium and add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> with your <strong>curry</strong> <strong>powder </strong>and<strong> ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
