    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>blanched peas </strong>to the pan with 75ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [115ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until the peas have warmed through</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p>",
