    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>with your <strong>flaked</strong> <strong>almonds</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>nutty</strong> <strong>spiced mushroom & pea rice</strong></p>",
